# {{lb|en|countable}} An [[abominable]] act; a [[disgusting]] [[vice]]; a [[despicable]] [[habit]]. {{defdate|First attested around 1150 to 1350.}}<ref name=SOED>{{R:SOED5|page=6}}</ref>
