# {{lb|en|countable}} That which is [[abominable]], [[shameful]]ly vile; an object that excites disgust and hatred; very often with religious undertones. {{defdate|First attested around 1350 to 1470.}}<ref name=SOED/>
#: {{syn|en|perversion}}
